<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Lenaddar Anatar</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-12 09:30:53</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Well, your close on the damage here. The spell starts out at 220 + 1 hp of damage per additional level AND 100 hps of stun damage to anything that is caught in its path - including yourself.<BR>
<BR>
Be sure to be well away from your target and duck if the intended mobs starts after you as you may end up in the spell radius not not resist it. Guess what? You too can go flying. Use levitate on yourself in close quarters before and this will negate the effect.<BR>
<BR>
This spell seems to work intensely well on light blues and Large sized targets (Ogres, Trolls and the like). Also remember that its an AoE so you can through 3-5? Gotten 4 close together up into the air. However this will advance you to most favored target status but not right away as they will be stunned out of there minds first.</font></td></tr></table>
